node.detail_zh: 患者於 7 月 18 日出現症狀，由檢疫中心送院，與第 #1533 宗個案患者有關連。（衛生防護中心於 7 月 22 日更新患者的年齡）
node.detail_en: The patient started having symptoms on July 18 and was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre. Her case is epidemiologically related to the case of patient #1533. (On July 22, the CHP updated the patient's age on file.)
node.classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
